snippet.title: Sengoku Basara HD Collection [PS3] Openings
snippet.description: One of the best HD remakes on the PS3 hands down. I just had to upload these amazing intros. Dont worry guys I'll make sure to feed you some gameplays from each of them. I literally have all Sengoku Basra games on the PS3 now thanks to my new PS3 ;) erm!
